So we needed to make the switch. There were just a couple issues. We didn't know R. I kind of

00:02:28.320 --> 00:02:32.960
used R in passing in the past, but I didn't know what the tidyverse was, I didn't know

00:02:32.960 --> 00:02:38.080
anything really, but we thought that shouldn't really be an issue. It's just writing things in

