00:08:05.200 --> 00:08:10.559
and then do the proper gluing where we pop those numbers into the table. So you can end up with

00:08:10.559 --> 00:08:16.720
pretty complicated, very cute looking tables using this glue syntax. It's pretty simple. So I love it.

